description: Meticulously updated designer condo in the heart of South Boston! You'll be wowed from the moment you step foot into this bi-level home. The main floor features an open, airy & bright kitchen/living space. The kitchen boasts oversized white shaker cabinets, quartz counters & Thermador appliances. Designer lighting, hardware & plumbing fixtures compliment the space. The front facing living room is anchored by custom built-ins & marble fireplace. Off the kitchen is the easily accessible, newly renovated bluestone patio just in time for spring. Rounding out this floor is a stunning updated bathroom & king-sized bedroom. You won't be able to wait to retreat to your serene primary suite at the end of a long day which encompasses the entire lower level. The bathroom drips in Carrara marble, designer lighting and fixtures. In addition to your custom walk-in closet, there is additional private storage just outside your unit door on this level. Don't miss this very special home close to it all!
